quran[9]{c,v,t}:
  40,41,"Eey mon yo yim…ďe am, ko wa…ói si mi…óo nodda on e da…óal, ho…óon nodda kam e Yiite?"
  40,42,"Hi…óon nodda kam e jeddugol Allah, sirkana mo e ko mi alanaa …óum ganndal, hara non, min mi…óo nodda on e pool…óo, cuhuroowo bakkaat Oon."
  40,43,"Sikke alaa, won'de ko noddoton kam e mum kon, dewal alanaa …óum aduna, wonaa La'akara. E won'de ruttorde men nden, ko ka Allah, e won'de ko fantim…ďe …ďeen, ngoni Yiite ngen."
  40,44,"Aray nde nganndoton, ko mi yewtata on kon; mi fawa fiyaaku am on e Allah. Pellet, Allah ko deen…óo jiyaa…ďe …ďen"."
  40,45,"Allah da…óndi mo, boneeji …ói …ďe pewjunoo, o fiiltii yim…ďe Fir'awna …ďeen, ko …ďuri bon'de e lepte."
  40,46,"Yiite ngen, …ďe mbee…ďitoyte e magge, bimmbi e kiikii…óe. √Ďande darnga daroytoo (wi'oyte): "Naatee yim…ďe Fir'awna …ďeen, ka …ďuri sa…ótude e lepte"."
  40,47,"JaŇčto tuma …ďe yeddondiroyta ka Yiite, lo'unoo…ďe …ďen wi'ana townitinoo…ďe …ďeen: "Minen, ko onon men jokkuunoo, taw si on du√Īanay men ge…óal e Yiite ngeen?""
  40,48,"Townitinoo…ďe …ďeen mbi'a: "En fof, hi…óen e magge. GooŇč…óii Allah √Īaawii hakkunde jiyaa…ďe …ďen"."
  40,49,"Won…ďe ka Yiite …ďen kadi mbi'ana ayninaa…ďe Jahannama …ďen: "Toranee min Joomi mon, O hoynana men, √Īalaande (wootere) e lepte …óen"."